Alternatively, if you'd like the JSON object to be more concise, here's an equivalent version:

```
{
  "people": [
    {"name": "Mark", "age": 19},
    {"name": "Joe", "age": 19},
    {"name": "Sam", "age": 30, "gender": "female"}
  ]
}
```
